-------------------------------------------------------------------
|    Operation    |    Async Method     |      Sync Method        |
-------------------------------------------------------------------
| 1. Read File    |  fs.readFile()      |  fs.readFileSync()      |
-------------------------------------------------------------------
| 2. Write File   |  fs.writeFile()     |  fs.writeFileSync()     |
-------------------------------------------------------------------
| 3. Append File  |  fs.appendFile()    |  fs.appendFileSync()    |
-------------------------------------------------------------------
| 4. Rename File  |  fs.rename()        |  fs.renameSync()        |
-------------------------------------------------------------------
| 5. Delete File  |  fs.unlink()        |  fs.unlinkSync()        |
-------------------------------------------------------------------
| 6. Create File  |  fs.writeFile()     |  fs.writeFileSync()     |
-------------------------------------------------------------------
| 7. Remove File  |  fs.rm()            |  fs.rmSync()            |
-------------------------------------------------------------------
| 8. Copy File    |  fs.copyFile()      |  fs.copyFileSync()      |
------------------------------------------------------------------- 